      "Virtue Creative Systems": "Virtue Creative Systems",
      "Virtue Creative Systems | Creative Workflow Software": "Virtue Creative Systems |创意工作流程软件",
      "Virtue Creative Systems builds focused creative software, starting with a native plugin manager for REAPER users.": "Virtue Creative Systems 构建专注于创意的软件，从为REAPER 用户提供的本机插件管理器开始。",
      "Virtue Creative Systems creates focused software for producers, engineers, sound designers, and technical creators, starting with Virtue FX Manager for REAPER.": "Virtue Creative Systems 为制作人、工程师、声音设计师和技术创作者创建了针对性的软件，从Virtue FX Manager 到REAPER 开始。",
      "Virtue Creative Systems home": "Virtue Creative Systems家",
      "Virtue Creative Systems is built around one idea: creative work should feel powerful, clear, and focused. The first product, Virtue FX Manager, is made for REAPER users who need a faster, more visual way to manage large plugin libraries without giving up local control.": "Virtue Creative Systems 围绕一个理念构建：创意工作应该让人感觉有力、清晰且专注。第一个产品Virtue FX Manager是为REAPER用户设计的，他们需要更快、更直观的方式来管理大型插件库而不放弃本地控制。",
      "Virtue Creative Systems starts with Virtue FX Manager: a native plugin manager for REAPER users who need faster search, better organization, visual thumbnails, notes, favorites, and track insertion.": "Virtue Creative Systems 以Virtue FX Manager 开头：为REAPER 用户提供的原生插件管理器，这些用户需要更快的搜索、更好的组织、可视化缩略图、注释、收藏夹和曲目插入。",
      "Virtue FX Manager": "Virtue FX Manager",
      "Virtue FX Manager combines plugin browser, favorites, thumbnails, notes, filters, categories, list/unlist control, and REAPER insertion in one focused tool.": "Virtue FX Manager 将插件浏览器、收藏夹、缩略图、注释、过滤器、类别、列表/取消列表控件和 REAPER 插入结合在一个集中工具中。",
      "Virtue FX Manager for REAPER": "Virtue FX Manager 为 REAPER",
      "Virtue FX Manager for REAPER | Virtue Creative Systems": "Virtue FX Manager 为 REAPER | Virtue Creative Systems",
      "Virtue FX Manager gives REAPER users a dedicated place to recognize plugins visually, remember why they matter, build favorites, filter by real workflow categories, and load tools into tracks without breaking the creative moment.": "Virtue FX Manager为REAPER用户提供了一个专门的地方来直观地识别插件，记住它们的重要性，建立收藏夹，按真实工作流程类别进行过滤，并将工具加载到轨道中，而不会破坏创意时刻。",
      "Virtue FX Manager interface preview": "Virtue FX Manager界面预览",
      "Virtue FX Manager is a native REAPER plugin manager for browsing, organizing, thumbnailing, noting, filtering, listing/unlisting, and inserting plugins faster.": "Virtue FX Manager 是一个原生REAPER 插件管理器，用于更快地浏览、组织、缩略图、注释、过滤、列出/取消列出和插入插件。",
      "Virtue FX Manager is a native REAPER plugin manager for visual plugin browsing, favorites, thumbnails, notes, filters, and insertion.": "Virtue FX Manager 是一个原生REAPER 插件管理器，用于可视化插件浏览、收藏夹、缩略图、注释、过滤器和插入。",
      "Virtue FX Manager is a native REAPER plugin manager that brings search, thumbnails, favorites, notes, filters, batch actions, and track insertion into one clean visual workflow.": "Virtue FX Manager 是一款原生 REAPER 插件管理器，它将搜索、缩略图、收藏夹、注释、过滤器、批处理操作和轨道插入引入到一个干净的可视化工作流程中。",
      "Virtue FX Manager is a native REAPER plugin manager that helps producers browse, organize, thumbnail, note, filter, favorite, list/unlist, and insert plugins faster.": "Virtue FX Manager 是一个原生REAPER 插件管理器，可帮助制作者更快地浏览、组织、缩略图、注释、过滤、收藏、列出/取消列出和插入插件。",
      "Virtue FX Manager is being prepared as a user-facing REAPER extension. Download links, installer notes, platform support, and setup instructions will be published here when the first public build is ready.": "Virtue FX Manager 正在准备作为面向用户的 REAPER 扩展。当第一个公共版本准备就绪时，下载链接、安装程序说明、平台支持和设置说明将在此处发布。",
      "Virtue FX Manager is being prepared as a user-facing REAPER extension. Join the early access list for release timing, first-build availability, and product updates.": "Virtue FX Manager 正在准备作为面向用户的 REAPER 扩展。加入抢先体验列表，了解发布时间、首次构建可用性和产品更新。",
      "Virtue FX Manager is designed around REAPER’s plugin cache and resource-path workflow. It supports the plugin formats REAPER stores in its library, including VST, VST3, AU, CLAP, JSFX, and architecture/cache variants where REAPER stores them. Exact platform support, installation steps, and release builds will be published with the first public release.": "Virtue FX Manager 是围绕 REAPER 的插件缓存和资源路径工作流程设计的。它支持REAPER存储在其库中的插件格式，包括VST、VST3、AU、CLAP、JSFX以及REAPER存储它们的架构/缓存变体。确切的平台支持、安装步骤和发布版本将随第一个公开版本一起发布。",
      "Virtue FX Manager is made for serious plugin collections: local thumbnails, local notes, safe cache rewriting with backup, high-DPI rendering, localization, user themes, and workflow controls that live inside REAPER.": "Virtue FX Manager 是为重要的插件集合而设计的：本地缩略图、本地注释、带备份的安全缓存重写、高 DPI 渲染、本地化、用户主题和 REAPER 内部的工作流程控件。",
      "Virtue FX Manager is made for the middle of the session, when a producer, DJ, composer, or mixer needs the right tool now. Visual thumbnails, favorites, notes, and filters help turn plugin choice from a menu hunt into a fast creative decision.": "Virtue FX Manager 是为会议中间制作的，此时制作人、DJ、作曲家或混音师现在需要正确的工具。视觉缩略图、收藏夹、注释和过滤器有助于将插件选择从菜单搜索转变为快速的创意决策。",
      "Virtue FX Manager native REAPER plugin manager interface with thumbnails, plugin list, and filter panels": "Virtue FX Manager 原生 REAPER 插件管理器界面，带有缩略图、插件列表和过滤器面板",
      "Virtue FX Manager release builds will appear here.": "Virtue FX Manager 发布版本将出现在此处。",
