      "When a session is moving, plugin hunting is friction. Virtue FX Manager makes the library visual, searchable, organized, and personal so creators can choose tools by recognition, favorites, notes, and color-coded tabs instead of memory and menu scrolling.": "当会话移动时，插件搜索就会产生摩擦。 Virtue FX Manager 使库可视化、可搜索、有组织且个性化，因此创建者可以通过识别、收藏夹、注释和颜色编码选项卡来选择工具，而不是通过内存和菜单滚动来选择工具。",
      "When will it be available?": "什么时候可以使用？",
