      "Yes. Virtue Creative Systems will expand into audio tools, plugin utilities, scripting apps, VFX helpers, and production utilities.": "是的。 Virtue Creative Systems 将扩展到音频工具、插件实用程序、脚本应用程序、VFX 帮助程序和制作实用程序。",
